author: Tom Hussain
title: The coronavirus outbreak may hurt Imran Khan's political future
description: There are increasing signs of disagreement between Prime Minister Imran Khan and the establishment in Pakistan.
content:
Populous Pakistan has not yet made the grim headlines spawned by the global coronavirus pandemic, despite reporting its first infections on February 26.
Sadly, in the weeks to come, it will. The number of infections is projected to spiral into the millions. … [+5872 chars]
